## Quick Reference — Apply Order

```bash
kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
kubectl apply -f service.yaml      # must include NEG annotation
kubectl get svcneg                 # verify NEG before ingress
kubectl apply -f ingress.yaml
kubectl get ingress -w             # wait for ADDRESS
```
